                                <a href="/builder-06"><i data-c-colour="c2" class="fas fa-edit"></i>Edit This in Step 06: Skills</a>
                            </div>
                            <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)">
                                <div class="job-builder-skill-review" data-c-border="all(thin, solid, grey)" data-c-padding="lr(normal)" data-c-radius="rounded">
                                    <div data-c-margin="tb(double)">
                                        <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Human Resources: Assessment Tools</p>
                                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Advanced</p>
                                        <p>Defined as: Ability to design and administer assessment tools and resources for staffing or academic purposes (e.g. exams, interview guides, course designs, user guides)</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div data-c-margin="tb(double)">
                                        <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Client Services</p>
                                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Advanced</p>
                                        <p>Defined as: Ability to communicate clearly and respectfully with service users, promoting client satisfaction, resolving issues and ensuring that the service is used effectively</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div data-c-margin="tb(double)">
                                        <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Initiative</p>
                                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Strongly in Evidence</p>
                                        <p>Defined as: Willingness to take on responsibilities and going above and beyond to take on challenges.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div data-c-margin="tb(double)">
                                        <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Ability to Collaborate</p>
                                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Strongly in Evidence</p>
                                        <p>Defined as: Ability to work with others to advance initiatives and build bridges within and across teams, generating mutual trust and respect.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div data-c-margin="tb(double)">
                                        <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Networking Abilities</p>
                                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Moderately in Evidence</p>
                                        <p>Defined as: Familiarity with the Canadian digital and high-tech community leading to quality of being trusted and having “street credibility”. Preference given to those who already have an established network connected to IT executives and CIO communities in Canada.</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div data-c-margin="tb(double)">
                                        <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Judgement</p>
                                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Strongly in Evidence</p>
                                        <p>Defined as: Ability to make considered decisions and come to sensible conclusions that respect the perspectives of all parties involved.</p>
                                    </div>
