                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div data-c-margin="tb(normal)">
                            <div data-c-grid="gutter middle">
                                <div data-c-grid-item="tp(1of2)" data-c-alignment="base(centre) tp(left)">
                                    <h5 data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-font-size="h5">Manager Information</h5>
                                </div>
                                <div data-c-grid-item="tp(1of2)" data-c-alignment="base(centre) tp(right)">
                                    <a href="/profile" target="_blank"><i data-c-colour="c2" class="fas fa-edit"></i>Edit This in Your Profile</a>
                                </div>
                                <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)">
                                    <div data-c-border="all(thin, solid, grey)" data-c-padding="normal" data-c-radius="rounded">
                                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(normal)">Johnny Ratha</p>
                                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(normal)">Director at Treasury Board of Canada Secretariat</p>
                                        <p>Ethical leadership and servant manager style. Creating an environment of psychological safety. Integrity, respect, trust, resourcefulness, and continuous learning are key values. Having meaningful work and fun is important too!</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div data-c-margin="tb(normal)">
                            <div data-c-grid="gutter middle">
                                <div data-c-grid-item="tp(1of2)" data-c-alignment="base(centre) tp(left)">
                                    <h5 data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-font-size="h5">Work Culture</h5>
