                                    <a href="/builder-01"><i data-c-colour="c2" class="fas fa-edit"></i>Edit This in Step 03: Work Environment</a>
                                </div>
                                <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1)">
                                    <div data-c-border="all(thin, solid, grey)" data-c-padding="normal" data-c-radius="rounded">
                                        <p>Our deadlines are usually close together, we balance some tasks at the same time, and our priorities change regularly. Our work keeps us on our toes! We have some middle management here but make most day-to-day decisions ourselves. Don’t be surprised to interact fairly often with our executives. Our work includes some administrative tasks are repeated on a regular basis. The tools we use work well for us but we are open to improving our processes. We spend a lot of our time engaging directly with the public, but there is also behind the scenes work to support others. Our team has diverse backgrounds, viewpoints, and skills and we play to each others strengths. We collectively own the team’s goals and are always looking for ways to pitch in.</p>
                                    </div>
